snippet.title: Sicko Sanctum 2 - 8 Return of the Baller (WIP)
snippet.description:
Here's a first look at the Baller's long waited return to Sicko Sanctum! They can heal using downed melee enemies and pack on immense pressure to the player, so it is very important to knock em out quick.
(Some animations may be redone and sfx are to be made)
